Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Nouvelle Entreprise",
  "subdomain": "nouvelle-entreprise",
  "category": 1
}


### Scï¿½nario 2: Gestion du cycle de vie d'une organisation
# 1. Crï¿½er organisation (voir ci-dessus)
# 2. Consulter les dï¿½tails
# 3. Dï¿½sactiver
# 4. Rï¿½activer
# 5. Supprimer


